  "text": "Then, it is sufficient to construct the perfect QSS (ε = 0) with d 4 Pauli operators for the channel N AB in the sense of PQC [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . In the case of our approximate QSS, the product channel of two RUCs (N AB = N A ⊗ N B ) just consume of half secret bits, so we say that it is efficient in weak sense (though small information is always leaking).",
